You slowly open your eyes. Blearily, you look around. You can see your sister, Fernkit, softly snoring beside you.

''Hey, Fernkit.'' Stretching out a paw, you prod your sister in the ribs. ''Fernkit wake up.''
Your sister impatiently bats you away.

''Go back to sleep Spottedkit.'' she yawns, flipping over to her other side.
What's your response?
> No
''No'' You mew. ''Come on. Pleeeaaassee???''
''Well, okay.'' Fernkit agrees, shaking moss off her pelt and trotting out the nursery.

You and Fernkit head out into the open. ''Well what should we do now?'' she asks, looking around. ''Nobody's up.
Which one do you want to do?
1: Get something to eat.
2: Go exploring.

