> 2
Swatting your Mouse a few mouse lenghts in front of you, quietly as you can, you begin stalking it.
''Hey, Fernkit!'' You call. ''Look at me. I'm hunting!
You crawl forward slowly on your belly then, when you're only one paw step away, you pounce.
Fernkit snorts. ''You call that hunting?'' she meows. ''Watch me. ''
Fernkit crawls stealthily forward towards the Mouse, then suddenly whirls around and leaps on top of you.
"Hey!" You yowl. "No fair!"
"First rule! " Your sibling mock growls from on top of you, "You have to surprise you prey!"
Soon in a flurry of fur, the two of you are tumbling over and over on the ground play biting at each other and batting at one another's ears. Soon you both collaspe on the ground.
''Ok.'' Fernkit pants. ''That's enough. Even though I do admit it was pretty fun.''she purrs, looking at you.
''So what should we do now?''
1: Go exploring.
2: Go back to the nursery.

> 1
Fernkit's eys twinkle with excitement. ''It's a good idea, but how are we going to get past the guard?''
How could you lure away the guard?
1: Maybe we could create a distraction.
2: Maybe we could find another way out.
3: Wait. What guard?
> 2
"Perhaps there's another way out of camp." You suggest.
''Oh!'' Fernkit's eyes light up as an idea pops into her mind.
"How about that hole by the dirtplace tunnel that Stonekit found yesterday?"
"That's perfect!" You exclaim, running over to the clump of reeds by the dirt place. "We just fit through."
Putting your head first, you squeeze through the hole and come out on the other side of camp.
''We made it!'' Fernkit gasps, exiting the hole after you. ''Come on. Let's explore!''
The two of you look around. ''C'mon! Lets explore.'' Fernkit mews. ''Lead the way!''
