Chapter Two
Play time

 Press any key to continue.

Sunlight filters in through the Nursery entrance, causing you to wake. With the memory of your previous adventure still fresh in your mind, you look around for your sibling.
The nursery is empty. They must be outside.
Use your compass to control your cat.

> out

> out
Outside the nursery, you can see the hunting patrol about to leave. Your mother, who was lying in the shade, pads over to you. "So you're finally up." She meows, swiping her tounge over your ear. "You've been asleep for quite a while."
You nod absentmindedly. ''Where's Fernkit?'' You ask.
Your mother jerks her muzzle towards the fresh kill pile. ''She's playing over there with Stone kit and Lilykit.''

"Ok!" You meow, bounding away.
"Stay out of trouble!" Your mother calls after you, but you hardly hear her.
As you arrive at the fresh kill pile, you can see your sister,Fernkit, Stonekit, and Lilykit rolling on the ground in a playfight. Your father, Dustpelt watches with interest from behind the fresh kill pile where he carefully selects a Vole to take to your mother, Ferncloud
"Hey guys! I wanna play too!" You call, racing over. Stonekit looks up from beneath his sister's paws. "Yeah!" He mews enthusiastically. "You can be on my team."
"Why can't I choose which team I want to be on?" You ask.
"Well...okay." Stonekit sighs, shuffling his paws. "But you have to be on either my team or Lilykit's team cos you guys are a moon older than us."
Who's team do you want to be on?
1: Stonekit
2: Lilykit

> 1

"Yes!" Stonekit purrs happily while Lilykit shrugs.
"It doesn't really matter who I get. They're both good players to me."
Padding to the fresh kill, he selects  a mouse and hooks it up with his claw. "Listen up! Here's how you play!" he yowls. " There are two teams! One team has to keep the mouse away from the other team. The other team, of course, has to try and get it. Ok?"
Stoekit nods at you. "We're the keep away team. Lilykit, you're the get the mouse team."
"Awww!" Lilykit pouts. "I'm always the get the mouse team! Why can't I be the keep away team?"
"Cos I said so." Stonekit retorts.
"It's not fair." Lilykit mutters.
"Life isn't fair." Stonekit retorts, "Now hush."
His sister scowls, but otherwise doesn't say anything as she makes her way back beside Fernkit.
"Now if there will be no futher interruptions," Stonekit continues, glaring at Lilykit "Lets start the game!"

1: Play!
> 1

Stonekit starts off with the mouse. He races around the freshkill pile with Lilykit tailing after him. "Catch!" He yowls at you, flinging it high over his head. You catch the mouse in your jaws and take off running as both Lilykit and your sibling advance towards you. Stonekit is running behind them, searching for a gap to break through.
Fernkit is nearly upon you. What do you do?

1: Toss the mouse back to Stonekit.
2: Hide behind Dovepaw.
3: Keep running.
> 1

"Stonekit! Catch!"
You spin around and toss the mouse high in the air. It goes up...up...up...
You relise with a jolt that you tossed it too high. Stonekit will never be able to catch it!
But as you turn, Stonekit races forward and does a flying leap. Twisting in mid air, he nabs the mouse and lands neatly back on his feet.
The rest of you stare at him in shock. "Stonekit that was amazing!" Lilykit gasps.
''For a second I thought you were a bird!'' Fernkit exclaims.
The blue-gray kit shifts his paws in embarrasment. "It was really nothing." He murmurs. "I just like jumping, thats all."
"Come on." you mew. "Let's keep playing."
Instantly, Stonekit races off with the mouse. You, Lilykit, and Fernkit hare after him.

